<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Ubuntu on LingLong</title><link>https://codetang-2417.github.io/tags/ubuntu/</link><description>Recent content in Ubuntu on LingLong</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>LingLong's Blog</copyright><lastBuildDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 11:38:45 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://codetang-2417.github.io/tags/ubuntu/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>ubuntu创建新用户并分配VNC远程桌面</title><link>https://codetang-2417.github.io/p/ubuntu%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E6%96%B0%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E5%B9%B6%E5%88%86%E9%85%8Dvnc%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E6%A1%8C%E9%9D%A2/</link><pubDate>Sat, 08 Jun 2024 09:56:31 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://codetang-2417.github.io/p/ubuntu%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E6%96%B0%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7%E5%B9%B6%E5%88%86%E9%85%8Dvnc%E8%BF%9C%E7%A8%8B%E6%A1%8C%E9%9D%A2/</guid><description>&lt;p>　　使用命令&lt;code>useradd&lt;/code>​。&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt"> 1
